Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:39.36,12k Outro Japanese,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Toki no suna kazoeteta, nani mo shirazu ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:50.57,12k Outro English,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}In a false dream I became speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:50.57,12k Outro Japanese,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Itsuwari no yume no naka, kotoba ushinau.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:24:01.89,12k Outro English,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}I would stare into the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:24:01.89,12k Outro Japanese,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Yureru manazashi, honou no naka de
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:12.16,12k Outro English,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}...as I swore to be true forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:12.16,12k Outro Japanese,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Chikau kokoro ha, itsu itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:23.51,12k Outro English,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Let my prayers be heard I will overcome hardship...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:23.51,12k Outro Japanese,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Kono inori todoke yo, fukai wadachi koete
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.95,0:24:34.69,12k Outro English,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}...and keep my oath until the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.95,0:24:34.69,12k Outro Japanese,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}Kono sekai no hate no, chikai mamori toosu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.74,0:24:54.27,12k Default Primary,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jsem zvyklý mít ruce potřísněné krví.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.41,0:24:57.90,12k Default Primary,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Takové věci už mně dávno nevadí.
